title: Frets on Fire - Rock Band Songs + Career Mode
description:
This torrent contains a .RAR file which contains all the songs from Rock Band (including the european exclusives) w/ drum and rhythm guitar/bass parts as well as a career mode for capable mods.

Notes:

-I'm new at making torrents, so forgive me if this one is a bit unstable.
